{"tid":2375986,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[垃圾廢國] 唔夠膽cut 走BNO人嘅中國籍","createTime":"2021-01-22T12:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T07:37:25.000Z","uid":56015,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"016e90fda7e9b0214a0ada7ad76a3063cb1efe0b","tid":2375986,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗稱BNO護照問題 並不知悉中央行動及措施<br />\n2021-01-22 <br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會會議今日在北京閉幕。全國人大常委譚耀宗表示，會議通過動物防疫法修訂草案、行政處罰法修訂草案、海警法草案，以及設立北京金融法院的決定草案的議案，會議集中研究內地的法例，並無關於香港議題。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗表示，就BNO護照問題，英國單方面毀掉中英雙方之間的協議，自己並不知悉中方的行動及措施，亦不想猜測，要視乎中央會否作出行動。若作出行動，中央會決定修改範圍的內容、方式及層次，強調自己無從猜度。<br />\n<br />\n至於香港議題未來會否在人大常委會會議或兩會討論，譚耀宗表示，按過去經驗，特區政府試過提出政府自行處理不到的議題，提請人大常委會處理，屆時人大常委會才會考慮，目前未聽到相關訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571848-20210122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571848-20210122.htm&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TSDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=e0d523f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571848-20210122.htm&h=ece09618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571848-20210122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c87890753e01f2347b87b20d85249db78e870e48","tid":2375986,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9575b2dddea4a9f4578eb5b491ef29ee9d2a7bf1","tid":2375986,"uid":389613,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"但另港共一面 Cut 飛機，另一方面又有中共海警法可以主動動武 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d311027e53543beb0bd9caeafeecb7924eb3735","tid":2375986,"uid":56015,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9575b2dddea4a9f4578eb5b491ef29ee9d2a7bf1","tid":2375986,"uid":389613,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"